IFREMER/CAPARMOR:
================

Vérifer que les modules suivants soient chargés:
-------------------------------------------------
Currently Loaded Modulefiles:
  1) intel-comp/11.1.073           2) netcdf-intel/3.6.3-11.1.073   3) intel-mpi/4.0.0.028

Compilation:
-----------
setenv MPI_INC /appli/intel/impi/4.0.0.028/include64
setenv MPI_LIB /appli/intel/impi/4.0.0.028/lib64

./configure --prefix=/home2/caparmor/grima/NH_MultiGrid --enable-mpi
make clean
make 
make install

Soumission:
----------
cd ../bin
qsub run_mgroms_caparmor.pbs
